channel.title: Pattaya Gogo: Escape From Alcatraz
channel.description: Escape from Alcatraz is a new video produced for Alcatraz GoGo Bar Pattaya. The video attempts to illustrate the paradox between escaping from Alcatraz and the surreal and subliminal dream state of staying inside with the GoGo girls.
